			"text":"## 최종 해결책\n\n```java\n// 1. MemberCoupon 락\nrepository.findByIdWithLock(id)\n\n// 2. Coupon 락\nentityManager.lock(\n  coupon, \n  PESSIMISTIC_WRITE\n)\n```\n\n✅ 테스트 통과!\n✅ useCount = 5",
